    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对坚果充满热情是一款生动且合作的“无压力”工厂模拟游戏，团队合作和精确度是成功的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个有趣且快节奏的体验中，玩家可以组队经营一个繁忙的工厂车间，选择专业工具，利用他们独特的技能来制造和交付日益复杂的零件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一起工作或独自工作时，目标是保持生产线高效运转，同时确保你的朋友们保持同步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你成功创造和交付的零件越多，赚取的金钱就越多，从而使你能够在公司旅程中不断进步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250220/extras/683ec334bdd4156bca274bc3ac7ed81c.poster.avif?t=1744262951\" width=800 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250220/extras/683ec334bdd4156bca274bc3ac7ed81c.webm?t=1744262951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250220/extras/683ec334bdd4156bca274bc3ac7ed81c.mp4?t=1744262951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250220/extras/296c048170e23b6709cba4fe139098aa.avif?t=1744262951\" width=800 height=178 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建你自己的制造公司</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁、购买和使用各种机器和设备</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动化你的生产</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义你的工厂布局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >个性化你的公司和合作团队</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色自定义系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买各种增益以提高你的速度和进度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买工厂建筑以制造不同的零件，赚取更多的金钱</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250220/extras/8649b8f0db3e05cb180efef2bbd68fe7.poster.avif?t=1744262951\" width=590 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250220/extras/8649b8f0db3e05cb180efef2bbd68fe7.webm?t=1744262951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250220/extras/8649b8f0db3e05cb180efef2bbd68fe7.mp4?t=1744262951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >适合休闲玩家和专注玩家的《对坚果充满热情》将机械加工和制造的挑战与有趣而引人入胜的氛围相结合。凭借其生动的艺术风格和动态的游戏玩法，工厂车间成为你的游乐场，让你掌握制作和交付完美产品的艺术。无论是与一群朋友合作还是独自一人，你都需要协调、快速反应和一个稳妥的计划，以确保一切顺利进行。准备好潜入一个充满工业乐趣的世界，看看在这个娱乐合作冒险中你能变得多“疯狂”吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250220/extras/7583e48b5a86e9617e3fde2ad0652858.poster.avif?t=1744262951\" width=596 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250220/extras/7583e48b5a86e9617e3fde2ad0652858.webm?t=1744262951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250220/extras/7583e48b5a86e9617e3fde2ad0652858.mp4?t=1744262951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
